  <file id="describe_pillar" brink:scope-id="0x0165978e0f9ffb2f">
    <unit id="describe_pillar:0" brink:hash="cb1679fd4762a382">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source><ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}" disp="Name(...)"/> is empty.</source>
        <target><ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}"/> no tiene nada.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="describe_pillar:1" brink:hash="0156a5788ee7b878">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>The <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}" disp="list"/> ring lies on <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}" disp="name(...)"/>.</source>
        <target>El anillo <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}"/> descansa sobre <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}"/>.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="describe_pillar:2" brink:hash="38d74fcc77208642">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>On <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}" disp="name(...)"/>, are the discs numbered <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}" disp="list"/>.</source>
        <target>Sobre <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}"/> se encuentran los discos <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}"/>.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
  </file>
  <file id="gameloop" brink:scope-id="0x018cd3641ffbd8ea">
    <unit id="gameloop:0" brink:hash="e5cee658bc6eb7f5">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>Staring down from the heavens you see your followers finishing construction of the last of the great temples, ready to begin the work.</source>
        <target>Desde los cielos observas a tus seguidores terminando la construccion del ultimo de los grandes templos, listos para comenzar la obra.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop:1" brink:hash="19a3d84c108a0a81">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source> Regard the temples</source>
        <target> Contemplar los templos</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop:2" brink:hash="db9d7c744e6c6454">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>You regard each of the temples in turn. On each is stacked the rings of stone. <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}" disp="describe_pillar(...)"/> <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}" disp="describe_pillar(...)"/> <ph id="s2" equiv="{slot 2}" disp="describe_pillar(...)"/></source>
        <target>Contemplas cada uno de los templos. Sobre cada uno se apilan los anillos de piedra. <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}"/> <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}"/> <ph id="s2" equiv="{slot 2}"/></target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
  </file>
  <file id="gameloop.move_post" brink:scope-id="0x01a7486876bf1b57">
    <unit id="gameloop.move_post:0" brink:hash="039452188f5abafd">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source> Move a ring from <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}" disp="name(...)"/> to <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}" disp="name(...)"/> </source>
        <target> Mover un anillo de <ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}"/> a <ph id="s1" equiv="{slot 1}"/> </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop.move_post:1" brink:hash="5998794078c67bcd">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source><ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}" disp="move_ring(...)"/></source>
        <target><ph id="s0" equiv="{slot 0}"/></target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop.move_post:2" brink:hash="ecf17f77dac60693">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>The priests far below construct a great harness, and after many years of work, the great stone ring is lifted up into the air, and swung over to the next of the temples.</source>
        <target>Los sacerdotes alla abajo construyen un gran arnes, y tras muchos anos de trabajo, el gran anillo de piedra se eleva por los aires y se balancea hasta el siguiente templo.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop.move_post:3" brink:hash="7779f0d89a1b5175">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>The ropes are slashed, and in the blink of an eye it falls once more.</source>
        <target>Las cuerdas se cortan, y en un abrir y cerrar de ojos cae una vez mas.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop.move_post:4" brink:hash="83f2791fca8d8256">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>Your next decree is met with a great feast and many sacrifices. After the funeary smoke has cleared, work to shift the great stone ring begins in earnest. A generation grows and falls, and the ring falls into its ordained place.</source>
        <target>Tu siguiente decreto se recibe con un gran festin y muchos sacrificios. Cuando el humo funerario se disipa, el trabajo de mover el gran anillo de piedra comienza en serio. Una generacion crece y cae, y el anillo desciende a su lugar designado.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop.move_post:5" brink:hash="b48966b9be8ba820">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>Years pass as the ring is slowly moved.</source>
        <target>Pasan los anos mientras el anillo se mueve lentamente.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="gameloop.move_post:6" brink:hash="3f92cfd38b69fe24">
      <segment state="translated">
        <source>The priests below fight a war over what colour robes to wear, but while they fall and die, the work is still completed.</source>
        <target>Los sacerdotes de abajo libran una guerra sobre el color de sus tunicas, pero mientras caen y mueren, el trabajo aun se completa.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
  </file>
